# Booking form email forwarding (Resend — https://resend.com)
# 1. Sign up at resend.com using mckenziemilburn13@outlook.com
# 2. Create an API key and paste it below (and add it in Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables)
# Leads are forwarded to the address in app/data/site.ts (site.email).
RESEND_API_KEY=

# Optional: custom "from" address once you verify your own domain in Resend.
# Leave unset to use Resend's no-setup onboarding sender.
# BOOKING_FROM="MLM Dressage <bookings@yourdomain.com>"
